Steps to Reproduce:

When C# string contains curly braces then highlighting breaks down afterwards. Code example (see highlighting after first string in code):

namespace Test
{
    class Test
    {
        string Test1 = string.Format("{0}", 1);
        string Test2 = string.Format("{0}", 2);
    }
}
